# Format:
# <trigger-id> : <text to speak>
#
# Use with trigger rules that emit source "O".
# Example in flash.rules:
# O 60010 1 : lamp_rising(23) && !attract

50001: Player one.
50002: Player two.
50003: Player three.
50004: Player four.

# Bonus x2
50005: Double bonus activated!

# Bonus x3
50006: Tripple bonus activated!

# Game Over
50009: Game over!

# Extra Ball
50007: Get the extra ball!
50017: Extra ball!

# Highscore
50010: New highscore!

# Shoot Again
50016: Shoot again!
